<p>To all our valued customers</p>

<p>The reality of the current COVID-19 crisis has definitely brought about changes to our daily lifestyles. As a business, we must respect the advice of the experts and be prepared to be innovative in how we respond to this crisis.</p>

<p>All our <a href="https://sweetsworld.com.au/candy-guides/easter-candy-australia/">Easter stock can be purchased online</a>. We have decided to remain open but we are also paying close attention to the daily advice from the government. We still have strict cleaning and sanitation controls in place to minimise any risk.</p>

<p>It's full steam ahead for us with the above measures in place and we still have full capacity for Easter chocolate eggs, bunnies, bilbies etc. Also we have gluten free, dairy free, sugar free, cocoa free ranges as well.</p>

<p>These are difficult times, however we believe that by supporting local businesses, everyone can do their part to help build a healthy and sustainable future for all Australians. We are here to assist with your requirements – large or small, so whether you're looking for <a href="https://sweetsworld.com.au/where-to-buy/bulk-lollies-australia/">bulk lollies for parties and events</a> or <a href="https://sweetsworld.com.au/where-to-buy/candy-gift-box-australia/">candy gift boxes for special occasions</a>, please do not hesitate to contact us for any upcoming projects that you require.</p>

<p>We wish you and your family the best health and we look forward to hearing from you.</p>

<p>Kind Regards<br>
Kards &amp; Kandy Team</p>

<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

<p><strong>Is Kards &amp; Kandy still open during COVID-19?</strong><br>
Yes, we remain open with strict cleaning and sanitation controls in place to minimise risk. We're committed to serving our customers safely while following government health advice.</p>

<p><strong>Can I buy Easter chocolate online instead of visiting in store?</strong><br>
Absolutely! All our Easter stock is available for online purchase at https://sweetsworld.com.au/product-category/easter/, including chocolate eggs, bunnies, and bilbies.</p>

<p><strong>Do you have Easter chocolate options for people with dietary restrictions?</strong><br>
Yes, we stock a full range of Easter chocolates including gluten free, dairy free, sugar free, and cocoa free options to suit different dietary needs.</p>

<p><strong>Can Kards &amp; Kandy help with bulk Easter orders for my business or event?</strong><br>
Yes, we have full capacity for large Easter orders and are here to assist with projects of any size. Please contact us to discuss your specific requirements.</p>

<p><strong>What Easter products do you currently have in stock?</strong><br>
We have full stock of Easter chocolate eggs, bunnies, bilbies, and other Easter treats, plus speciality ranges including gluten free, dairy free, sugar free, and cocoa free varieties.</p>

